        <h2 class="asset-name entry-title"><a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/ham-to-share-so.html" rel="bookmark">Ham to &#8220;share something&#8221; about Ark Park</a></h2>
        <div class="asset-meta">
            <span class="byline">
    
                By 
                <span class="vcard author"><a class="fn url" href="http://www.mines.edu/~mmyoung">Matt Young</a></span> on <abbr class="published" title="2014-02-24T18:20:55-06:00">February 24, 2014  6:20 PM</abbr>
    
            </span>

            <span class="separator">|</span> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/ham-to-share-so.html#comments">24 Comments</a> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/ham-to-share-so.html#comment-last">(new)</a>
            

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="asset-content entry-content">

        <div class="asset-body">
            <div class="kw-format"><p>Don’t hold your breath, but Ken Ham, who is in Nashville for a religious broadcasters’ conference, plans an <a href="http://blogs.answersingenesis.org/blogs/ken-ham/2014/02/24/in-nashville-but-not-to-sing/" rel="external "> announcement about the Ark Park</a>. 
</p>

<blockquote class="kw-quote"><div class="kw-quote-body"><p>I have a few media interviews lined up over the next couple of days to discuss the debate [with Bill Nye] and also to share something about the Ark Encounter.</p>

</div></blockquote>

<p>
Dare we speculate?</p>

</div>


        </div>



        <div class="asset-more-link">

  
            Comment on &ldquo;<a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/ham-to-share-so.html#comments-open" rel="bookmark">Ham to &#8220;share something&#8221; about Ark Park</a>&rdquo;.
  

        </div>
