                By 
                <span class="vcard author"><a class="fn url" href="http://www.mines.edu/~mmyoung">Matt Young</a></span> on <abbr class="published" title="2014-02-17T12:00:00-06:00">February 17, 2014 12:00 PM</abbr>
    
            </span>

            <span class="separator">|</span> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/coccinella-sept.html#comments">2 Comments</a> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/coccinella-sept.html#comment-last">(new)</a>
            

