<div class="kw-figure" style=" width:606px;"><div class="kw-figure-img"><img src="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/02/16/SamarasingheB.Coccinella_septempunctata.JPG" alt="SamarasingheB.Coccinella_septempunctata.JPG" width="600" height="518" /></div>
<p><big><a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coccinella_septempunctata" rel="external "><em>Coccinella septempunctata</em></a> – seven-spotted ladybird beetle. Also, ladybug, <a href="http://www.biocontrol.entomology.cornell.edu/predators/Coccinella.html" rel="external ">lady beetle</a>. Scotland, UK.</big>   
