            </span>

            <span class="separator">|</span> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/01/texas-public-sc.html#comments">7 Comments</a> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/01/texas-public-sc.html#comment-last">(new)</a>
            

