    </div>
    <div class="asset-content entry-content">

        <div class="asset-body">
            <div class="kw-format"><p>That is the title of a <a href="http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/science/2014/01/creationism_in_texas_public_schools_undermining_the_charter_movement.html" rel="external ">Slate article</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zack_Kopplin" rel="external ">Zack Kopplin</a>.  But actually it is much worse (see also <a href="http://ncse.com/news/2014/01/creationism-texas-charter-schools-0015318" rel="external ">NCSE’s take</a> here). Here are the first 3 paragraphs of Kopplin’s article.</p>

