        <h2 class="asset-name entry-title"><a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/01/freshwater-reco.html" rel="bookmark">Freshwater: Reconsideration denied</a></h2>
        <div class="asset-meta">
            <span class="byline">
    
                By 
                <span class="vcard author">Richard B. Hoppe</span> on <abbr class="published" title="2014-01-22T11:57:05-06:00">January 22, 2014 11:57 AM</abbr>
    
            </span>

            <span class="separator">|</span> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/01/freshwater-reco.html#comments">28 Comments</a> <a href="http://pandasthumb.org/archives/2014/01/freshwater-reco.html#comment-last">(new)</a>
            

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="asset-content entry-content">

        <div class="asset-body">
            <div class="kw-format"><p>The Ohio Supreme Court today denied John Freshwater’s motion to reconsider his appeal of the decision to terminate him as a middle school science teacher in the Mt. Vernon City Schools.  This brings to an end the involvement of the state courts in the affair. (I’m on a mobile and can’t post a link to the case page-someone can do so in a comment.)</p>

<p>Freshwater’s only remaining possibility is to convince the U.S. Supreme Court to grant cert. It’s not known whether he or the Rutherford Institute will attempt that.</p>

</div>


        </div>



        <div class="asset-more-link">

  
