  easy-to-circulate PDF version go </span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><a href="http://www.evolutionarymanifesto.com/man.pdf"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">here</span></a></span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">
  (34 pages)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">For further technical justification of
  the evolutionary trend to increasing cooperation, see my book
  Evolution&#8217;s Arrow which is </span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><a href="http://users.tpg.com.au/users/jes999/EvArrow.htm"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">here</span></a></span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">For more technical detail on the
  future evolution of consciousness see Stewart, J. E. (2007) <i style="">The future evolution of consciousness</i>,
  Journal of Consciousness Studies, Vol. 14, No. 8, Pp. 58-92.<span style="">&nbsp; </span>Also see ECCO Working Paper No. 10 of 2006
  which is online </span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><a href="http://cogprints.org/5270/1/Consciousness-Evolution.pdf"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">here</span></a></span></b><b style=""><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><span style="">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 28pt; color: red;"><a href="../../../Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/Desktop/John/WebSite/EVOLVE/Feb%202004/19.htm"></a><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>
  </td>
